<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 01:46:08 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>银行集团称参议院稳定币奖励提案“不足”</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-05/bank-groups-say-senate-stablecoin-rewards-proposal-falls-short</link><description>银行集团周一推迟了一项加密货币市场结构提案，这加大了美国立法者继续就关键稳定币奖励条款进行谈判的压力。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i8DHz477Madk/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 00:55:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-05/bank-groups-say-senate-stablecoin-rewards-proposal-falls-short</guid></item><item><title>人工智能最热门的私营公司拥有蓬勃发展的加密影子市场</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-05/ai-s-hottest-private-companies-have-booming-crypto-shadow-market</link><description>向散户投资者出售人工智能热潮的一部分的竞赛已经成为主流——封闭式基金、区间基金、特殊用途工具。现在，加密货币平台正在提供与地球上最有价值的私营人工智能公司相关的交易——普通投资者几乎没有其他方式可以参与这些交易。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/idJ8est2Gn.M/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 00:30:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-05/ai-s-hottest-private-companies-have-booming-crypto-shadow-market</guid></item><item><title>全球加密货币竞赛正在将分裂的欧洲抛在后面</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2026-05-04/global-crypto-race-why-divided-europe-is-losing-ground</link><description>&lt;p&gt;在货币未来的争夺中，美元拥有巨大的领先优势&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i1mTEn6hIX1g/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 21:00:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2026-05-04/global-crypto-race-why-divided-europe-is-losing-ground</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚养老金体系内部的风险支点</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-04/crypto-property-grow-in-australia-s-self-managed-funds-smsfs</link><description>&lt;p&gt;对退休的深深焦虑促使人们转向自助投资工具，他们在其中购买了加密货币和其他风险资产。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ikmOe9DG3alA/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 21:00:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-04/crypto-property-grow-in-australia-s-self-managed-funds-smsfs</guid></item><item><title>与特朗普相关的世界自由组织起诉孙宇晨诽谤</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-04/trump-linked-world-liberty-sues-justin-sun-for-defamation</link><description>世界自由金融公司表示，正在以诽谤罪起诉贾斯汀·孙(Justin Sun)，指责这位亿万富翁加密货币企业家在上个月对特朗普相关项目提起诉讼后，针对该项目发起了协调一致的媒体宣传活动。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iAw0svHpP.xU/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 13:08:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-04/trump-linked-world-liberty-sues-justin-sun-for-defamation</guid></item><item><title>比特币自 1 月份以来首次升至 80,000 美元以上</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-04/bitcoin-btc-tops-80-000-for-three-month-high-as-asian-stocks-rise</link><description>由于人们对达成协议以解决中东冲突扫清道路的预期不断波动，比特币自 1 月份以来首次突破 80,000 美元。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iw.jWHIx1AUg/v2/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 02:58:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-04/bitcoin-btc-tops-80-000-for-three-month-high-as-asian-stocks-rise</guid></item></channel></rss>